In terms of the integration story, Bill touched on the strong growth across all of those businesses.
And I think they're really starting to see that resonate very well with customers.
And, in fact, as we had anticipated when we were talking about anticipating 2010, Office 2010, that was going to be a key part of the story, and I think we're starting to see that play out, early days, which I think can sustain for a while.
