I also think underlying that are some real technical improvements we've made within the search engine, the algos are better, and the investments we're making are really allowing us to monetize at a higher level.
We also saw some strengths in a few other geos, which helped increase the performance there.
So I do believe that trend we expect to continue into Q2.
