And I think we've made great progress as a team.
I think you're seeing that both in the long-term guidance and in, frankly, our day-to-day execution through the quarter.
SATYA NADELLA:  And I would just add that we are also making pretty significant changes in just the very workflow of our engineering teams, and that also leads to us getting more out of our current investment.
So there is significant, I would say, combination of culture change, as well as how we work change that drives more innovation for same dollar.
